open_data_grading.analysis: The data is from the official government site of the Nuevo León State, which consistently updates the dataset. All the information is available online in a machine-readable and reusable format (CSV files). The data is openly licensed and can be accessed free of charge. The site has clearly communicated the update schedule. It was relatively straightforward to find information about this dataset, although navigability could be slightly improved. Data identifiers are provided for the key elements in the dataset.
